Biom data table

biom_sub2k_150bp.Rd

This a 975-sample subset of the EMP (Earth Microbiome Project) observation table containing 150bp-length sequences. The samples were picked randomly and evenly across 17 habitats and then evenly across studies in each sample type.

biom_sub2k_150bp

Format

Data frame with columns

sequence

Observation-sequence found.

807.W.S.12.b

Sample name.

2382.RU006.C181.RH.2.383.root.9.11.lane1.NoIndex.L001.sequences

Sample name.

...

Sample names.

Source

https://earthmicrobiome.org/

Examples

  str(biom_sub2k_150bp)
